ownedComment.body:
Ontology about the micro-domain of the Offering of Passenger Rail Chatered Services.
This ontology describes the service offering, an specific subdomain of Passenger Rail Chartered Domain, which has two other variants: the touristic and commemorative freigh, which are not in the scope of the model.
The ontology is based on the paper published in EDOC 2013, from Nardi et al., about the services core ontology, UFO-S.
Note that the <<partOf>> relation does not belong to OntoUML, but has been used with the same semantics of the one in Figure 1 of Nardi's paper.
